Package: CREx
Type: Package
Title: Control interactive visual-audio presentation from R.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lorenz Weise
Maintainer: Lorenz Weise <lorenz-weise@gmx.net>
Description: CREx allows controlling interactive visual-audio presentations
    from R. CREx works by providing R-wrapper functions for underlying C-functions,
    which use the SDL2 C-library for controlling graphics, sound and user interaction.
    Essentially, CREx is a very simple SDL interface.
